world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on January 1, issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -7 degrees C., max. 2 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 6 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., clear to drizzle,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 24 degrees C., max. 34 degrees C., clear, calm to
