<HEADLINE> Macao Unemployment Rate Drops </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, December 31 (Xinhua) -- Unemployment rate in the
September-November period this year dropped to 2.9 percent in
Macao, latest statistics show.
</P>
<P>
Figures released by the Macao Census and Statistics Department
of Macao on Wednesday say that jobless rate dropped 0.1 percent
from the August-October period to reach 2.9 percent.
</P>
<P>
The jobless rate in the same period last year was recorded at
4.2 percent.
</P>
<P>
The underemployment rate was recorded at 0.9 percent, down 0.2
percent from the August-October period. But it was a 0.2 percent
rise from the same period last year.
</P>
<P>
The department said the figures were based on sample surveys it
took between September and November.  
</P>
