<HEADLINE> Six Parliamentarians Fail to Cast Vote in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, December 31 (Xinhua) -- The polling of the
Presidential election closed at 15:00 (local time) Wednesday
afternoon. However, Six Parliamentarians failed to cast their
votes at the Parliament House.
</P>
<P>
