Taiwan Straits and help realize the direct mail, shipping and
trade between the two sides of the straits," he urged.
</P>
<P>
Taiwan authorities should also make an early response to the
mainland's serious appeal for negotiations under the "one China"
principle, he added.
</P>
<P>
With regard to world affairs, Jiang said that the ever-closer
global economic links and the rapid scientific and technological
progress worldwide are offering a historic opportunity for the
economic development of all countries.
</P>
